name: Immortal Smile
description:
From collection "lost times"

Lasting smile
On the glass of your face
Thin as spring flowers
Sweet as honey
Permanent frame
one smile
A look
Which remains in your heart
Lasting sound
In a corner of your mind
Constantly repeating a smile
And a gentle melody
From a delicate sweet feeling
And an image that never ends
The color does not fade
And it is not lost
A picture of eternity
